# paint.type AI Manifest (Level 2)

This is the AI manifest for the `src/backends/` directory (Level 2) of paint.type.

## Purpose

paint.type backends

## Authority Split

- **Central protocol authority:** `standards/` repository
- **Local integration authority (this directory):** `src/backends/` specific configuration

